STATE of North Carolina
v.
Douglas PAGE, Jr. No. 373P06. Supreme Court of North Carolina. July 14, 2006. Douglas Page, Jr., Pro Se. William P. Hart, Senior Deputy Attorney General, Edward W. Grannis, Jr., District Attorney, for State of NC. Prior report: 169 N.C.App. 127 , 609 S.E.2d 432 .

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Defendant on the 13th day of July 2006 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Cumberland County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 14th day of July 2006."
